TO DEPLOY TO A LINUX SYSTEM:
*** Secret credentials must be copied into ~/.bashvars (from home machine)

This files are to be installed in other locations when deploying to Linux systems:
  -- dot_bash_profile to ~/.bash_profile
  -- nginx.conf to /etc/nginx
  -- RP to /etc/nginx/sites-available
  ** ...and then symlinked to sites-enabled:
  % sudo ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/RP /etc/nginx/sites-enabled
  *** The IP address of the server must be correct in /etc/nginx/sites-available/RP
